description	"Imperial Engineer

^2Weaponry:
- SE-14C Blaster Pistol (2)
- Blast Cannon
- 3 Detonation Packs

^6Inventory:
- Advanced Medpac (50HP+) ^3[CS4]

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^8[CS1]
- Slap ^3[CS2]
- Ammo Dispenser ^3[CS3]

The Imperial Engineer, is the repairman unit for the Galactic Empire. His primary weapon shoots a wide spray of bolts that will eliminate enemies easily from short range."